{"type": "article", "id": 29595, "title": "Levi's 表现依然平平，Stüssy 与 Porter 又推了联名包包｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-14T03:41:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 23371, "name": "销售额"}, {"id": 26337, "name": "鞋履"}, {"id": 30174, "name": "皮革制造商"}, {"id": 30175, "name": "季度财报"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 3120, "name": "Levi's"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}, {"id": 29617, "name": "AG"}, {"id": 30176, "name": "Trapstar"}, {"id": 30177, "name": "Material Girl"}, {"id": 8603, "name": "麦当娜"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714105039G1lfiKDgE6kS5HUC.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/hermes-pierre-hardy-minority-stake-in-pierre-hardy-10487509/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hermès&nbsp;收购 Pierre Hardy 品牌少数股权</b></a><b></b>｜Hermès 最近宣布收购设计师 Pierre Hardy 同名奢侈鞋履品牌少数股权，此位设计师从 1990 年就开始参与爱马仕鞋履设计随后扩展至珠宝，以抓人眼球的几何图案、前卫的鞋履设计闻名。这一巴黎品牌在巴黎、纽约和日本设有店铺，并刚刚将品类扩展至手袋。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/weaker-pound-boosts-burberry-first-quarter-retail-sales-problems-persist-10487843/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Burberry 一季度销售额小幅上涨</b></a>｜受到“脱欧”及后续英镑汇率大跌的影响，英国奢侈品牌 Burberry 在截至 6 月 30 日的一季度内，零售收入上涨了 4% 至 4.23 亿英镑（约合 6.09 亿美元），超出预期。但品牌所面临的问题依旧存在，同比销售额下跌 3%，亚太、欧洲及美国区都有单位数字的可比销售额下跌。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Chanel-acquires-Richard-tannery-specialist-in-lamb-skin,713093.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Chanel 收购高端羊皮制造商</b></a>｜Chanel 日前宣布收购专门制造高端羊皮的家族企业 Richard tannery，后者 1852 年创立于法国，此前 Chanel 已拥有其多数股权。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Levi-s-remains-flat-in-Q2-international-business-thrives-as-US-struggles,713003.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Levi’s 二季度表现平平</b></a>｜Levi’s 发布截至 5 月 29 日的二季度财报，其中美国市场净收入有 4% 的下跌，欧洲区和亚洲区则分别有 8% 和 12% 的上涨。美国地区直营销售额有所上涨，批发份额则呈下跌状态。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/denim/ag-hires-margaret-maldonado-director-of-women-ready-to-wear-10485905/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>AG 任用新女装成衣总监</b></a>｜优质牛仔品牌 AG 聘请 Margaret Maldonado 担任品牌女装成衣部门总监，后者曾创立时尚品牌 L’Agence 及个人同名时尚、美妆代理公司。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">Madewell 发布<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/7/13/12172184/madewell-preorder-fall-collection-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋季 lookbook</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714093820jHZOWEkngQPFmLC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660340\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714093821Zh5W2xjGp8ESqgtJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635390\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714093821pTiucU2NmdaP76Ok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714093823XFQlpNse586MbGVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653921\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://nitrolicious.com/2016/07/12/puma-x-trapstar-london-autumnwinter-2016-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Puma 和伦敦生活方式品牌 Trapstar 合作了一个秋冬系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092602Jpawm70zxnEg52or.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092603HZ46YKRWcyqAxDJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092603biaFEBczjyr6PTfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092603FpZDhs8znKdHe1kX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092604kWuiSwAfvs0xgMUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.788710\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092605zkgHIFyto0cbln1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092605aqBQsRjJbZmHVcX6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593012\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714092605yQM45HGZufw2vdj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754019\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>麦当娜与女儿一同创立的时尚品牌 Material Girl 几个月前邀请年轻女歌手 Pia Mia 担任创意总监，近日又发布了 Pia Mia 出镜的秋季 lookbook：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714103811PcRMwX43FDhY7odz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714103815V3aqTb5KPIc1fhlg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714103817vtDz9uEQgSeyfGbV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690430\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">比利时设计师&nbsp;Tim Coppens 个人同名男装品牌昨日在纽约时装周<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/7/tim-coppens-ss17\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布 2017 春夏系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095150BTmHIJpxuq7VQeyN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095151sW3h0xqlVcYK7Bmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071409515221VvRKT7iq5OFJsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095152vqOfjCb2z6FKW08V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095153ilvgpTG3fCjKZx67.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095153MG0wUE9v5buYAIQe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">此外，他上月被运动品牌 Under&nbsp;Armour 任命为新产品线 UAS 系列的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27776.html\">执行创意总监</a>，此次<a href=\"http://solecollector.com/news/2016/07/under-armour-sportswear-club-low\" rel=\"nofollow\">穿着一双&nbsp;UAS Club Low 新品球鞋亮相</a>：</p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714095641ucZI78o14HUqYt3l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">街头潮流品牌&nbsp;Stüssy 与包袋品牌 Porter 继续合作，推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/stussy-porter-2016-summer-beach-pack-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">夏季沙滩系列包袋</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607141003052AhgJRLowYbzyCSt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714100307DoqbUQugjP92B3Kd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714100307lQT08WapvhSuwfHR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714100308Jt7CBnuGMVzreqE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714100308Tulvx9OqGpRMoIU0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607141003085pvJKVOu8Ye0MrTm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">奢侈品电商 Net-a-Porter 此前为庆祝与澳洲品牌 Zimmerman 合作十周年，<a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/news/net-a-porter-and-zimmerman-launch-an-exclusive-col.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布了联名系列</a>，包含一些泳装及蕾丝裙等：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607141012229dvsfJmYDj4C1oeZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617234\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714101223aqExgrUYM9RZlkCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714101224MH1OxnS7ZQ5sdrvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.093750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607141012242ebNVpXDOW630Exc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.093750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">A Bathing Ape 发布 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/a-bathing-ape-2016-fall-winter-eyewear\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬眼镜系列</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714094215rAp9FqJbS3Ov4CTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714094216XoHSFdZKvcLD3Akh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714094217WQaG0VENcLhCtIDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714094221MK7JBSkAXlGYrmZc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}